Metwit,is,a,real,time,crowdsourced,social,weather,application,Users,can,share,information,about,the,weather,through,tags,and,applications,and,users,can,search,for,weather,by,location,The,Metwit,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Metwit,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,sending,and,receiving,weather,information,retrieving,weather,information,by,location,and,accessing,metatags,associated,with,weather,reports